replies.body:
> I would really like it if Naut's size increased greatly when his w is active. Another champion that also needs a size increase is{{champion:82}}. The lore describes him an 8 foot tall metal juggernaut, yet in game he is shorter than most normal humans like {{champion:236}} and {{champion:104}}

That's a good point.

I don't know about his W change, though. It doesn't make much sense thematically for him to grow when he uses his shield.
